snippet.title: Marvel's Avengers - Spider-Man With Great Power Cinematic Trailer | PS4, PS5
snippet.description:
"Avengers, assemble. Bad guys, scatter!" Peter Parker works with the Avengers to stop AIM from getting new and definitely deadly technology.

Play Spider-Man throughout the Avengers Initiative when he swings in to Marvel's Avengers on November 30 for PS4 and PS5!
